ProblemSolution
The indicator lamp blinks, but the battery does not charge.There is dirt on the battery terminals: Clean the terminals with a soft, dry cloth (�� 43). The battery has been charged many times: Select BATTERY AGE to view the battery age; if the battery is old, replace it with a new battery ( ≡ 336). If the battery still fails to charge, contact your Fujifilm dealer ( 420).
The power supply icon is not displayed.Confirm that POWER SUPPLY ON/COMM OFF is se- lected for USB POWER SUPPLY/COMM SETTING.
